 convection are the same.
 Therefore for simplicity we focus on the conditionally averaged Boussinesq
 equations:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray}
\frac{\partial\sigma_{i}}{\partial t}+\nabla\cdot\sigma_{i}\mathbf{u}_{i} & = & \sum_{j\ne i}\sigma_{j}S_{ji}-\sigma_{i}S_{ij}\label{eq:sigma}\\
